msgctxt "56_Unleashing Heat Actions"
msgid ""
"When you are in danger of being caught, the <Sign:35> icon will sometimes "
"appear in the upper right corner of the screen. Press "
"<Action:Button_Triangle@Chase> in time to stop and fight off the pursuer "
"with a Heat Action."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Unleashing Heat Actions"
msgid ""
"Successfully executing a Heat Action will temporarily stop the enemy in "
"their tracks.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"However, as Heat Actions can only be used <Color:7>once per chase "
"event<Color:Default>, use it as a last resort."
msgstr ""